16:18.482 --> 16:20.033
No, no, no, no. It's fine.

16:21.276 --> 16:22.353
It's...

16:22.964 --> 16:24.243
Perfect.

16:43.700 --> 16:45.745
This place is incredible.

16:45.888 --> 16:48.080
