18:09.800 --> 18:12.100
So we're just gonna
have to be a little more...

18:13.728 --> 18:14.626
Listen.

18:15.761 --> 18:16.767
What is it?

18:17.500 --> 18:18.810
Chora.

18:24.300 --> 18:25.800
Chora?

18:26.730 --> 18:27.914
That's your bully?

18:28.792 --> 18:29.807
She's a girl!

18:30.017 --> 18:31.508
