if you're sitting next to us

19:39.100 --> 19:40.680
but not, you know, with us.

19:40.800 --> 19:42.480
We wouldn't want it
to be awkward.

19:42.600 --> 19:45.000
Oh, perfect. Okay.
I love this now.

19:52.400 --> 19:55.480
- How the hell did you get in here?
- I followed the flower delivery guy.

19:55.600 --> 19:58.980
Don't worry. Your wife
is out getting waxed.

19:59.100 --> 20:00.480
I'm sorry.

20:00.600 --> 20:01.680
I meant your sister.

20:01.800 --> 20:04.280
- What the hell is this?
- Publicity stunt.

20:04.400 --> 20:06.080
You kissed
Ryan "creepo" casdale.

20:06.200 --> 20:07.980
