more often than I do?

20:19.972 --> 20:21.166
He's a boy.

20:22.116 --> 20:23.139
He's a baby.

20:23.712 --> 20:24.772
You're my man.

20:25.500 --> 20:28.315
You're my big man.

20:29.128 --> 20:30.275
You didn't sleep with him?

20:30.395 --> 20:32.380
I fell asleep a few times
while he was talking,

20:32.500 --> 20:34.452
- but that's about it.
- Promise?

20:35.200 --> 20:36.504
I promise.

20:37.300 --> 20:38.241
I do.

20:38.361 --> 20:39.386
Here.

20:49.663 --> 20:51.380
Wait, wait.
I have to tell you something.

20:51.500 --> 20:52.588
What?

20:53.075 --> 20:55.280
