20:55.400 --> 20:58.000
Yeah. But I have to
tell you something.

21:09.800 --> 21:11.024
Don't you ever knock?

21:11.144 --> 21:12.484
That's your girlfriend?

21:12.604 --> 21:14.780
I was gonna tell you about it.
I swear.

21:14.900 --> 21:17.080
So those tickets
to "babes in toyland,"

21:17.200 --> 21:18.657
