21:20.100 --> 21:23.120
- They were subterfuge and a gift.
- And you!

21:23.240 --> 21:25.488
- What?
- Weren't my bangs enough?

21:25.615 --> 21:27.469
Oh, it was a completely
different approach-

21:27.589 --> 21:29.580
- get out of my house, you whore!
- Let it go.

21:29.700 --> 21:31.520
Can't we just all talk
about this like adults?

21:31.640 --> 21:33.280
Get her drippy butt
out of my house!

21:33.431 --> 21:35.173
- No!
- What?

21:36.727 --> 21:38.195
She's not leaving.

21:39.559 --> 21:40.577
This is...

21:40.991 --> 21:43.312
Utterly mortifying.

21:43.754 --> 21:44.766
This is...

21:44.886 --> 21:46.980
The worst thing
that's ever happened.

21:47.100 --> 21:49.580
Juliet, you are my sister,
and I love you.

21:49.700 --> 21:51.292
But I can't choose sides.

21:54.173 --> 21:55.306
Well, guess what.

21:56.400 --> 21:57.725
