Karen, really.

22:28.300 --> 22:30.080
I don't think
you do either, Lisa.

22:30.200 --> 22:33.180
I've known him for a long ti--
longer than you, and I--

22:33.300 --> 22:36.484
well, I remember Nick and I
walking on the beach

22:37.011 --> 22:39.237
and the way the sun
hit your hair. It just...

22:39.768 --> 22:41.031
Glistened.

22:41.151 --> 22:42.297
Signore George.

22:42.997 --> 22:43.825
Yeah.

22:43.945 --> 22:46.280
Would you follow me,
please, to the tasting room?

22:46.485 --> 22:48.080
Yeah, I guess

22:48.200 --> 22:50.957
you asked for
the chiavennasca.

22:51.077 --> 22:52.876
Yeah, I did.

22:52.996 --> 22:54.920
