23:32.200 --> 23:33.875
This the chiavennasca?

23:33.995 --> 23:36.900
No, no. It's vin ordinaire.

23:43.069 --> 23:44.854
So you're Dutch's boy?

23:46.000 --> 23:47.043
Yeah.

23:48.400 --> 23:49.455
I guess so.

23:50.220 --> 23:52.310
For what do you seek?

23:53.253 --> 23:55.680
When my dad died, his briefcase
was full of information

23:55.800 --> 23:58.100
