23:59.200 --> 24:00.894
Incriminating information.

24:01.213 --> 24:03.180
Elder, as in
the techno-philanthropist?

24:03.300 --> 24:04.400
Yeah.

24:07.114 --> 24:09.851
Any idea why he might have
had a file like that?

24:12.200 --> 24:13.780
Did I do something wrong?

24:13.900 --> 24:15.780
I'm sorry.

24:15.900 --> 24:18.680
If you are who you say you are,
I will find you.

24:18.800 --> 24:20.069
If not, well.

24:21.020 --> 24:22.880
Those are your bad dreams.

24:23.000 --> 24:24.177
Arrivederci.

24:27.000 --> 24:28.780
Me wearing
the superman underoos

24:28.900 --> 24:30.380
and he's wearing
wonder woman.

24:30.500 --> 24:32.183
I'm not kidding.

24:32.303 --> 24:33.560
There he is.

24:33.680 --> 24:36.300
Hi, baby. Just in time.

24:38.658 --> 24:40.219
- What's going on?
- We can go.

24:40.400 --> 24:43.680
No. We've moved on
to spirits.

24:43.800 --> 24:46.281
Nick,
we're drinking grappa.

24:48.611 --> 24:50.746
Maybe the two of you
have had enough?

24:51.800 --> 24:54.788
Loosen up, baby.
We are in India.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.281
We are?

24:56.500 --> 24:58.043
What did I just say?

24:58.163 --> 24:59.880
You said we were in India.

25:00.000 --> 25:01.000
Nick.

25:01.734 --> 25:03.256
It's grappa.

25:06.421 --> 25:07.886
Remember?

25:08.800 --> 25:10.954
Remember what?
What about grappa?

25:11.754 --> 25:13.141
We had a couple of bottles

25:13.261 --> 25:15.268
the night
that Nick proposed to me.

25:19.904 --> 25:21.232
Nick proposed to you?

25:21.352 --> 25:23.880
- You didn't tell her?
- When would that have come up?

25:24.000 --> 25:25.445
When did he propose to you?

25:25.565 --> 25:27.880
When we were 19.
Why didn't you tell her?

25:28.000 --> 25:29.734
You're so secretive.

25:30.191 --> 25:31.368
Because we were 19.

25:31.488 --> 25:34.079
Exactly. We were 19.
It's ancient history.

25:34.199 --> 25:35.880
It was down by the lake,
just down--

25:36.000 --> 25:38.208
down the hill
from where we're all staying.

25:38.328 --> 25:40.900
And we...
I don't know, we'd been,

25:41.200 --> 25:43.480
like, sailing all day
or playing tennis.

25:43.600 --> 25:45.680
I just remember him saying
that he--

25:45.800 --> 25:47.580
he knew it wasn't
gonna be easy

25:47.700 --> 25:50.780
because I was so rich
and he wasn't.

25:50.900 --> 25:53.765
But he knew we were
supposed to be together.

25:53.885 --> 25:56.393
Hey, Karen, can we...

25:56.513 --> 25:59.020
Oh, let her finish.
Let her finish.

25:59.140 --> 26:01.356
And then we, you know,

26:01.476 --> 26:03.780
we drank a bunch of grappa.

26:03.900 --> 26:05.985
- And, um...
- Lisa.

26:06.105 --> 26:09.100
- You know, just spent time...
- Lisa, I should've told you.

26:13.000 --> 26:14.580
Thanks.

26:14.700 --> 26:15.912
I'm sorry.

26:19.700 --> 26:21.292
God,
you are a bitch sometimes.

26:21.412 --> 26:24.100
I know.
It's a problem.

26:32.885 --> 26:34.426
Lisa come on. I was 19.

26:34.546 --> 26:37.000
I was in Italy.
I was drunk on grappa.

26:37.521 --> 26:39.080
Everyone proposes
when they're 19.

26:39.200 --> 26:41.580
- It didn't mean anything.
- Well, it meant something to her.

26:41.700 --> 26:43.426
