would've meant something

26:43.546 --> 26:44.769
if she'd said yes.

26:44.889 --> 26:47.017
Lisa, it was a thousand years ago.

26:47.214 --> 26:49.480
When we started dating,
we exchanged plenty of stories

26:49.600 --> 26:51.680
about our old boyfriends
and girlfriends, remember?

26:51.800 --> 26:53.873
- Yeah, so?
- There must have been some reason

26:54.000 --> 26:55.871
you decided to leave
this particular one out

26:55.992 --> 26:58.037
unless maybe you forgot.
Did you forget?

27:01.500 --> 27:02.580
I don't understand

27:02.700 --> 27:04.789
why you don't just go
to the headmaster

27:04.909 --> 27:07.380
and tell him this bullying
is taking place.

27:07.500 --> 27:09.373
Because the little orphan
is never gonna learn

27:09.495 --> 27:12.180
- how to stick up for himself.
- Like you learned?

27:12.300 --> 27:13.967
18 years of being beat up by girls,

27:14.118 --> 27:16.600
and what's his revenge?
The ministry.

27:17.400 --> 27:19.780
- That's awful.
- Every summer, your Uncle Brian

27:19.900 --> 27:21.980
would come back from vacation
with aunt Deirdre

27:22.100 --> 27:23.880
and cousin derinda
covered in bruises.

27:24.000 --> 27:25.101
It was tragic.

27:25.221 --> 27:27.680
What did they call you again?
The princess?

27:27.800 --> 27:29.516
What did they call you again,
fatty-paddy?

27:29.636 --> 27:31.380
I wouldn't mind
a change subject.

27:31.500 --> 27:34.680
I swear, sometimes I don't know
where you children come from.

27:34.800 --> 27:37.800
Why did you really enter
the church, Uncle Brian?

27:38.300 --> 27:41.680
I didn't see anywhere else
in the world I fit in.

27:41.800 --> 27:45.580
I didn't want to pursue business
or politics.

27:45.700 --> 27:48.780
I never...
Felt really well liked.

27:48.900 --> 27:50.880
So a life of leisure
didn't seem appealing.

27:51.000 --> 27:52.880
You need friends
for that kind of thing.

27:53.000 --> 27:55.580
So, you know, I guess
I really never felt

27:55.700 --> 27:58.100
a part of the human family.

28:01.849 --> 28:03.562
Well, thank you
for your honesty.

28:03.900 --> 28:06.284
Ellen, thank you.

28:09.867 --> 28:11.314
Take it easy, sailor.

28:11.434 --> 28:13.218
You're gonna overheat
your blood.

28:14.200 --> 28:15.151
Sorry.

28:15.271 --> 28:18.651
I haven't seen a child
pepper food that vigorously

28:18.785 --> 28:20.532
since you were a boy, Brian.

28:21.400 --> 28:23.000
Bon appetit.

28:26.100 --> 28:27.480
You should probably
answer that.

28:27.600 --> 28:29.180
