grappa party or something.

28:37.199 --> 28:38.080
Pronto?

28:38.200 --> 28:40.434
Mr. George.
Harold Templeton.

28:41.166 --> 28:43.096
May we convene?

28:45.000 --> 28:47.080
I apologize for my abrupt exit
the last time.

28:47.200 --> 28:50.280
But you can never be too sure
who's who in my line of work.

28:50.400 --> 28:52.180
Your father
would've understood.

28:52.300 --> 28:54.816
He was...
Also a complex man.

28:55.400 --> 28:56.681
What happened?

28:57.347 --> 28:58.778
Three months ago,
he asked me

28:58.898 --> 29:00.880
