on Simon elder--

29:01.000 --> 29:02.080
anything vexing.

29:02.200 --> 29:03.780
What for?
To blackmail him?

29:03.900 --> 29:06.680
I never asked.
It was not my concern.

29:06.800 --> 29:08.449
But when your father
came to me a 2nd time

29:08.544 --> 29:10.623
and asked me to perform
similar due diligence

29:10.743 --> 29:12.959
on Tripp Darling,
well, I realized

29:13.079 --> 29:14.580
he was walking
for someone else,

29:14.700 --> 29:16.415
so I washed my hands
of it.

29:19.300 --> 29:23.080
So who was my father
working for? Do you know?

29:23.200 --> 29:25.380
Did he ever mention someone
that he referred to

29:25.500 --> 29:26.842
by the letter "c"?

29:28.401 --> 29:29.401
No.

29:30.600 --> 29:32.200
Not that I recall.

29:33.044 --> 29:36.707
And there's your chiavennasca
for Mr. Darling.

29:43.600 --> 29:45.778
- Hey.
- Hey

29:46.738 --> 29:48.457
