about earlier.

29:48.577 --> 29:49.579
You know what?

29:49.700 --> 29:51.718
Save it for someone who cares.

29:54.858 --> 29:56.880
I don't want these shoes
anymore. You know why?

29:57.013 --> 29:59.380
- They don't fit?
- No, actually, they fit fine.

29:59.500 --> 30:01.980
I don't want these shoes
because these shoes--

30:02.100 --> 30:04.480
these $1,200 shoes--

30:04.600 --> 30:06.804
and for everything that is
selfish and foul

30:06.924 --> 30:08.880
and consumptive
and creepy about you.

30:09.000 --> 30:11.913
Nick and I have...
A daughter.

